     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet BehandlingsresponsCML</b></p><a name=\"BehandlingsresponsCML\"> </a><a name=\"hcBehandlingsresponsCML\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentResponseEvaluation.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/TreatmentResponseEvaluation</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentResponseEvaluation.html#TreatmentResponseEvaluation-complete_hematological_response\">complete_hematological_response</a></td><td>Komplet hæmatologisk respons (CHR)</td><td>Complete Hematological response (CHR)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentResponseEvaluation.html#TreatmentResponseEvaluation-complete_cytogenetic_response\">complete_cytogenetic_response</a></td><td>Komplet cytogenetisk Respons (CCyR)</td><td>Complete cytogenetic response (CCyR)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentResponseEvaluation.html#TreatmentResponseEvaluation-partial_cytogenetic_response\">partial_cytogenetic_response</a></td><td>Partiel cytogenetisk Respons (PCyR)</td><td>Partial cytogenetic response (PCyR)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentResponseEvaluation.html#TreatmentResponseEvaluation-major_molecular_response\">major_molecular_response</a></td><td>Major molekylært Respons (MMR)</td><td>Major molecular response (MMR)</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-none\">none</a></td><td>Ikke målbar molekylær sygdom</td><td>None - used to choose none of the available values</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-v2-0532.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0532</code></a><span title=\"Version is explicitly stated to be 3.0.0\"> version ?3.0.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-v2-0532.html#v2-0532-UNK\">UNK</a></td><td>Uoplyst</td><td>unknown</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
